      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54B32 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six, delivering linear power delivery up to its 8,000 RPM redline. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from documented rear subframe reinforcement and refreshed bushings. Power is channeled through a precise 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M-differential. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul and valve clearance adjustment, ensuring the high-pressure VANOS unit and valvetrain operate strictly within factory tolerances. While the exterior shows minor evidence of its road-going heritage, the mechanical integrity and throttle response remain exceptionally sharp for the purist driver.",
